watchmetrics

gary.smith@ed.ac.uk
15 05 2020

A program for comparing watchman fill cocktails
using performance mertics.

How to run

Firstly you have to have output files from 
rat stored in a watchmakers folder naming 
convention - see GetFilePath() 

Then, after changing the file paths 
as necessary, do

$ root
root [0] .L watchmetrics.cc+
// compare cocktails for IBD positrons
root [1] Draw_Multi_hNhits(11)
// ................. for IBD neutrons
root [2] Draw_Multi_hNhits(2112)
// ................. for 208Tl PMT glass
root [3] Draw_Multi_hNhits(208)
// compare particles for 3 pct WbLS
root [4] Draw_Multi_hNhits(0,3)